/**
 * Make first row or thead element top sticky.
 *
 * Table classes:
 * - sticky-header: sticky first row.
 * - sticky-header-multi: sticky thead; headers moved via sortable + JavaScript.
 *
 * Tested:
 * - Windows 10: (all skins) Chrome, Firefox, Edge.
